WEBVTT

00:01.336 --> 00:02.684
KLAUS: Previously on "The Originals"...

00:02.714 --> 00:04.986
FREYA: If this prophecy is fulfilled,

00:05.016 --> 00:06.354
you will all fall.

00:06.384 --> 00:09.324
One by friend, one by foe, and one

00:09.354 --> 00:10.825
by family.

00:10.855 --> 00:13.344
As this mark grows, you'll go mad.

00:13.374 --> 00:16.397
You'll become a relentless ripper.

00:16.427 --> 00:17.460
REBEKAH: Hide my body.

00:17.462 --> 00:18.479
Elijah, do it!

00:18.509 --> 00:19.671
(Gasps)

00:20.548 --> 00:22.631
(Whooshing)

00:25.169 --> 00:26.785
- (Gasps)
- ELIJAH: What the hell did I just see?

00:26.787 --> 00:28.208
Vincent told me he found a way

00:28.238 --> 00:29.876
to extract the serum from Aurora.

00:29.906 --> 00:31.490
If Marcel becomes the beast,

00:31.492 --> 00:32.741
then I won't be able to stop him.

00:32.743 --> 00:34.076
Davina was like a daughter to me,

00:34.078 --> 00:36.136
and you condemned her to
a fate worse than death.

00:36.166 --> 00:37.951
So you will never be safe.

00:37.981 --> 00:40.231
I am nothing less than your worst...

00:40.261 --> 00:41.985
(Sharp squish)

00:43.037 --> 00:44.537
KLAUS: No!

00:45.389 --> 00:46.212
HAYLEY: What happened?

00:46.242 --> 00:47.178
ELIJAH: It's Marcel.

00:47.208 --> 00:48.646
I took his life.

00:50.661 --> 00:52.500
VINCENT: Marcel took that serum
the moment I offered it to him.

00:52.530 --> 00:54.520
So if the Mikaelsons think he's dead,

00:54.550 --> 00:56.293
they're in for a hell of a surprise.

00:57.903 --> 01:01.131
(Crickets chirping)

01:08.412 --> 01:10.362
KLAUS: You're a survivor.

01:10.364 --> 01:13.285
And survivors need names.

01:14.502 --> 01:16.168
How about Marcellus?

01:16.170 --> 01:17.386
Marcellus?

01:18.989 --> 01:22.407
Family can be more than just
those with whom we share blood.

01:22.709 --> 01:24.843
We can choose.

01:31.435 --> 01:32.690
I can't do it.

01:32.720 --> 01:34.495
Now, you once said the
same thing of your reading.

01:34.525 --> 01:35.976
Devote yourself to your music.

01:36.006 --> 01:38.173
Soon you shall be Johann Sebastian Bach.

