18:52.738 --> 18:55.656
He wants you to come back here
and stand trial for your sins.

18:56.909 --> 18:59.493
Before a jury of those
who hate me the most?

18:59.495 --> 19:01.078
Like hell I will.

19:01.080 --> 19:03.080
