a dagger in my chest.

28:48.998 --> 28:53.256
You see, my brother, he
cannot handle the brutal truth

28:53.763 --> 28:58.456
that he destroys everything he touches.

29:01.294 --> 29:05.796
You murdered our mother.

29:06.377 --> 29:08.432
And both of your fathers.

29:09.014 --> 29:12.303
