29:29.559 --> 29:31.722
But I have had no such relief.

29:33.225 --> 29:37.394
Chained to him not
because of a sire link,

29:37.396 --> 29:40.703
but because of a foolish pact
that we made to each other

29:40.733 --> 29:43.517
when we were nothing more than children.

29:45.854 --> 29:50.857
